# 🌦️ Weather App

A simple weather web app that lets you check current weather conditions by city name using the OpenWeatherMap API.

## 🛠️ Built With
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- OpenWeatherMap API

## 🔥 Features
- Search weather by city
- Dynamic icon + background based on weather
- Responsive card design
- Real-time temperature, wind & humidity

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Clone the repo
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

